{
  "texts": [
    "Our primary goal in this broad area was to present the most significant and creative contributions.",
    "Reference to recent developments, methodological precision, a variety of techniques (ML, DL, and MHO), and the application of modern datasets were among the selection criteria.",
    "By doing this, we want to maintain the manageability of our review and offer insightful information without becoming excessively complex.",
    "By adopting this approach, we were able to examine these techniques' performance, drawbacks, and potential for improvement in greater detail, which helped us to draw a clearer picture of where AI is headed in cybersecurity today and in the future.",
    "Thousands of contributions have been made; however, our selection process concentrated on those that offer noteworthy breakthroughs and valuable applications for identifying CCF attacks.Our objective search approach focused on important review articles about fraud attack detection in order to collect a wide variety of studies."
  ]
}